    "Experiments within CREOLA can validate or discredit architectures and prompt approaches in a safe sandbox environment before clinical deployment.",
    "Our experiment results show that omissions are more common than hallucinations (3.45% to 1.47%, respectively).",
    "However, hallucinations were much more likely to be classified as a \"major\" error compared to omissions (44% to 16.7%, respectively).",
